Otto KRUPP, Appellant-Petitioner,
v.
NEW JERSEY STATE PAROLE BOARD, Respondent-Respondent. C-782 September Term 2017
080650 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 4, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004700-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
